data.description: Spacious home w/detached garage/workshop (35x20) Well-maintained & move-in ready. You'll love the space this home has to offer.  Updates include metal roof (2018), water filtration/softener & reverse osmosis system (maintained annually by Tri-State Water); 20 Gal Pressure Tank & Well Pump, both w/5 yr warranty (11/2022); pest control (inspected annually by Dodson Pest Control); Goodman Heating & Air system (2019) (maintained semi-annually by Barber Heating & Air), water heater (2020); smooth-top range & refrigerator to remain; washer & dryer--do not remain; 15x12 covered deck on back and 8x30 deck on front, split bedroom floor plan, with formal dining room, the primary bedroom has 2 WIC & ensuite bath, built-in shelving on each side of the fireplace (fireplace is inoperable due to no hookup to propane gas (seller does not warrant system). RING cameras do not remain (possibly negotiable).
